OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOvercast
OL,6,Fwith widespread low cloud soon
OL,7,Fdeveloping into the evening. Outbreaks
OL,8,Fof rain will spread northwards across
OL,9,Fthe region during the night, some of
OL,10,Fwhich are likely to be heavy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA cloudy but mostly dry start,
OL,13,Fwith isolated showers developing
OL,14,Fthrough the morning, some of which
OL,15,Fcould be heavy and thundery at times.
OL,16,FWinds generally light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
